data.text:
Seeems like Manufacturer has changed the name of the product (to After Shave Balm),and changed the package color to white without changing product quality (and not changing the price .... !); It serves the purpose for me. I like it.
What bothers me is the fact that store selling the product completely missed this change and continue selling it under old name and showing it at AMAZON with the same image without any comment/explanation and therefore .... confusing the customers;
I am sure manufacturer (Vichy, France) and distributor (Vichy, Canada) would not be happy about it, because this might have significant number of customers start looking for different product, from different manufacturer.
